class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fadc29fa6d4a85b3b278803e7b2b6305ee08e06a","tid":2198214,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75384800b3d2d5ea1f3016eb58e0627b35a80aeb","tid":2198214,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08:08:15.000Z","msg":"黃翊呢個樣都食個康子妮既話真係天大新聞<br />\n<br />\n好彩假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08:22:40.000Z","msg":"你講完我先覺得係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n始終假又何必出來澄清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要係咁問有冇人影到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513b4fa0fb048ca68dfbf2a19f51ac670a916c07","tid":2198214,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77192cccd66ee55da595644b496be92960149b9d","tid":2198214,"uid":309553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T07:59:03.000Z","msg":"細so有冇份"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08:37:33.000Z","msg":"細So精蟲上腦，見侵兩面排緊(隊)<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"190d1dd52692567251ee7c7721e7f7b30a008a0b","tid":2198214,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08:43:57.000Z","msg":"【愛的替身？】傳康子妮拍MV撻着黃翊 老婆陳存正淡然：最重要唔好搞到頭家<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200911/3UM7W74VGFCHBA3M52NFOVR5FM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200911%2F3UM7W74VGFCHBA3M52NFOVR5FM%2F&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=c46c85ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200911%2F3UM7W74VGFCHBA3M52NFOVR5FM%2F&h=9c5e386b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200911/3UM7W74VGFCHBA3M52NFOVR5FM/</a>"},{"pid":"0211b0386af6249d06793ec980a05e3b4f13fac6","tid":2198214,"uid":198900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T11:57:42.000Z","msg":"遭前度女友怒斥狗男女<br />\n林曉峰死撐康子妮唔係第三者<br />\n<br />\n文： 音樂小組 29/06/2002<br />\n<br />\n林曉峰早前公開與康子妮的戀情，兩人更大方合照。誰知此舉觸怒前度女友潘菁華，更怒罵林曉峰與康子妮是「狗男女」。林曉峰昨日揚言早已跟前女友講清楚分手，並死撐康子妮並非第三者。<br />\n<br />\n林曉峰昨日知悉遭前度女友潘菁華公開指摘後，第一時間接受電台訪問，其間阿Lo（林之洋名）堅稱康子妮並非第三者，更強調自己從沒負過任何人，他說︰「兩個女人並唔認識，我同佢（指潘菁華）冇聯絡，有個咁問題，大家都冇可以講。（有冇同前女友講清楚分手？）有。（康子妮係咪第三者？）唔係。（仲有冇經濟上支持前女友？）唔講，講錢好核突，對大家都係個唔好經驗。」<br />\n不會主動聯絡前女友<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隨後阿Lo堅決表明不會為此主動聯絡潘菁華，他說︰「唔好再挑起任何人怒氣啦！對佢講，今次係唔愉快經驗，人講我乜都得，我不嬲都冇形象，我娛樂圈工作都係搵啖飯食，總之我對得住老闆、朋友同身邊人。（你都兜得幾好呀！係咪承認新戀情？）所有人問我都認。（係咪同前女友分手？）係。」<br />\n阿Lo又力指刊登該篇報道的雜誌「作」，旨在趕絕自己，他說︰「唔好再騷擾佢（指潘菁華），呢本雜誌作！我都係搵飯食！唔希望有人趕絕我。本雜誌記者根本乜都唔知，問問題又好有挑釁性。」最後問阿Lo與潘菁華分開不久，即與康子妮拍拖，似乎不太好，他說︰「Timing係唔好，不過我不嬲都唔理啦﹗<br />\n<a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/channels/ent/20020629/20020629011549_0003.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fchannels%2Fent%2F20020629%2F20020629011549_0003.html&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=0b5ccc6a\" target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/channels/ent/20020629/20020629011549_0003.html</a>"},{"pid":"529cea4ed1ce461a2069e50082558480b0989ef3","tid":2198214,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:08:59.000Z","msg":"黃太o既回應<br />\n<br />\n好有骨咁"},{"pid":"4bfe9c450147